title: Slaughtering of Calves for Germany
notes:
Data Are For Federally Inspected Calves Under Three Months Old. Data For October 1918 On Exclude Alsace-Lorraine; For July 1922 On Exclude The Saar And Other Surrendered Territory. Data For 1935 Include Uninspected Calves From Bavaria, And Saar. Source: Data For 1904-1915, 1919-1937: Vierteljahrshefte Zur Statistik Des Deutsches Reichs, 1906, Iii, Pp. 40-41; 1907, Ii, P. 241, 1908, Ii, P. 205; Successive Issues. Data For 1916-1918: Vierteljahrshefte Zur Statistik, Erganzungshefte 1916-1918, Pp. 51-81.

This NBER data series m01045 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
